#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:4 e81e470007ab4ccf948a85af060a37aa
msgid "翻译 Godot-FmodPlayer"
msgstr "Translating Godot-FmodPlayer"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:6 04bb005aac7447d88e5b3bb020b8200d
msgid ""
"Godot-FmodPlayer 的文档和插件界面都需要稳定的翻译维护。翻译贡献不只是把中文逐句替换成英文，更重要的是保持术语、API "
"名称、示例代码和页面结构一致。"
msgstr ""
"Both the Godot-FmodPlayer documentation and plugin interface need stable "
"translation maintenance. Translation contributions are not just about "
"replacing Chinese sentences with English; more importantly, they keep "
"terminology, API names, example code, and page structure consistent."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:9 e9e6915b8faa432a8c4b79e5eb498371
msgid "在线文档翻译"
msgstr "Online Documentation Translation"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:11
#: 8c8cc2b6a1594e3bb340c094bd76fb97
msgid ""
"在线文档使用 `Sphinx <https://www.sphinx-doc.org/en/master/>`_ 构建，源文件位于 "
"``source/``，格式为 reStructuredText。"
msgstr ""
"The online documentation is built with `Sphinx <https://www.sphinx-"
"doc.org/en/master/>`_. The source files are in ``source/`` and use the "
"reStructuredText format."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:13
#: 07219a5614684fafb594a1d188d21b58
msgid "英文文档通过 gettext / PO 文件维护。请不要直接复制一份英文 ``.rst`` 来翻译，否则后续中文源文档更新时很难同步。"
msgstr "The English documentation is maintained through gettext / PO files. Do not copy the ``.rst`` files into a separate English version, because that makes future updates from the Chinese source documentation difficult to synchronize."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:15
#: 091561ba8b2b4e838078fe6e227117f3
msgid "常用流程如下："
msgstr "The common workflow is:"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:17
#: f97aec19204747ec942fb16f19f665c7
msgid ""
"sphinx-build -b gettext source build/gettext\n"
"sphinx-intl update -p build/gettext -l en"
msgstr ""
"sphinx-build -b gettext source build/gettext\n"
"sphinx-intl update -p build/gettext -l en"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:22
#: 921df8d8a4344d27aa0edb8c2c804b34
msgid "翻译文件位于："
msgstr "Translation files are located at:"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:24
#: c5a2c27bdea94e43994d400492aca7c7
msgid "locales/en/LC_MESSAGES/"
msgstr "locales/en/LC_MESSAGES/"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:28
#: 5ccfa54ebb63475ca4bef776b08130dd
msgid "修改 ``.po`` 后，编译并构建英文 HTML："
msgstr "After editing ``.po`` files, compile them and build the English HTML:"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:30
#: d80da96d01d644d89fdc41dcb2f8fd39
msgid ""
"sphinx-intl build -l en\n"
"sphinx-build -b html -D language=en source build/html_en"
msgstr ""
"sphinx-intl build -l en\n"
"sphinx-build -b html -D language=en source build/html_en"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:35
#: 4bbe4706e9c649128ce3d70c25d253d6
msgid "翻译时请注意："
msgstr "When translating, keep these points in mind:"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:37
#: c966348b15204e779054d91342088a28
msgid "``msgid`` 保持不变，只修改 ``msgstr``。"
msgstr "Keep ``msgid`` unchanged and edit only ``msgstr``."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:38
#: bcfcba1d316d421fb5180a4bd3c3ca48
msgid "API 类名、方法名、属性名和枚举名不要翻译。"
msgstr "Do not translate API class names, method names, property names, or enum names."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:39
#: cdefe037638e465888a95a2ea444c744
msgid "``:ref:``、``:doc:``、```code```、链接和 GDScript 示例要保持可构建。"
msgstr "Keep ``:ref:``, ``:doc:``, ```code```, links, and GDScript examples buildable."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:40
#: 66c98afe6cb44dadab5119ce85894f19
msgid "中文术语请优先参考 :doc:`../glossary`。"
msgstr "For Chinese terminology, refer to :doc:`../glossary` first."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:41
#: d46178f871f24d1f8c8ce63daf577998
msgid "如果源文档改了标题或标记，记得重新生成 gettext 模板并更新 PO。"
msgstr "If titles or markup change in the source documentation, regenerate the gettext templates and update the PO files."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:44
#: 0756ec8aecbb40b68b38788cc4b9c40f
msgid "离线文档翻译"
msgstr "Offline Documentation Translation"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:46
#: a6751abe67ea474d8b9e82dc77c5e94b
msgid "离线类参考文档使用 XML 风格的类描述。它更接近 Godot 官方类参考格式，适合编辑器内提示、类说明和属性描述。"
msgstr "The offline class reference uses XML-style class descriptions. It is closer to Godot's official class reference format and is suitable for editor hints, class descriptions, and property descriptions."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:50
#: d71db2420ae34f3daea005063429a1f2
msgid ""
"`Godot class reference primer "
"<https://docs.godotengine.org/en/4.x/engine_details/class_reference/index.html"
"#doc-class-reference-primer>`_"
msgstr ""
"`Godot class reference primer "
"<https://docs.godotengine.org/en/4.x/engine_details/class_reference/index.html"
"#doc-class-reference-primer>`_"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:52
#: a4e8a7558b274970807b632d2d606cfd
msgid "维护离线文档时，请保持 API 名称与 GDExtension 绑定一致。新增类、属性、方法或枚举后，应同步检查在线文档与离线文档是否都已更新。"
msgstr "When maintaining offline documentation, keep API names consistent with the GDExtension bindings. After adding classes, properties, methods, or enums, check that both the online and offline documentation have been updated."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:55
#: b8c862892bb04a9e8c329584801f59cf
msgid "属性本地化"
msgstr "Property Localization"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:57
#: f9efe9337aa0400caaec054fcd650c82
msgid "插件属性本地化用于编辑器检查器中的显示名称、分组和提示文本。它与在线文档翻译不是同一套文件。"
msgstr "Plugin property localization is used for display names, groups, and tooltip text in the editor Inspector. It does not use the same files as the online documentation translation."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:59
#: 3117aa6925de46fe8beac722c31f2c32
msgid "如果你修改了导出的属性名、分类或提示文本，请同时检查："
msgstr "If you change exported property names, categories, or tooltip text, also check:"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:61
#: 89fceca4e3b740d7bd575c02d76d0a9e
msgid "GDExtension 绑定中的属性名称。"
msgstr "Property names in the GDExtension bindings."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:62
#: 40a44d50d9394e3a9f3648ffb229d7f5
msgid "编辑器中实际显示的本地化文本。"
msgstr "The localized text that is actually displayed in the editor."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:63
#: 6f703dd694a24e14a74235ecab53644c
msgid "在线 API 文档中的属性说明。"
msgstr "Property descriptions in the online API documentation."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:66
#: f84fba7f9638466ab1523cf381bfdf07
msgid "翻译检查"
msgstr "Translation Checks"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:68
#: 632f4deba6b44eac9f662560d13f9474
msgid "提交翻译前建议至少检查："
msgstr "Before submitting translations, check at least:"

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:70
#: e2ec20b1b4f540a38fb83a6aaacfe213
msgid "英文 HTML 能否成功构建。"
msgstr "Whether the English HTML builds successfully."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:71
#: c3027355577342e08ebaec7569eda9af
msgid "页面中是否残留明显中文。"
msgstr "Whether any obvious Chinese remains on the page."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:72
#: 32be11025805424fb8f844ca38b51533
msgid "是否存在 ``msgstr \".\"``、``#, fuzzy`` 或明显机器翻译残留。"
msgstr "Whether there are any ``msgstr \".\"`` entries, ``#, fuzzy`` markers, or obvious machine translation leftovers."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:73
#: 6a86eb79f8f34d298b0c2257d17c35dd
msgid "代码块、内部引用和表格是否渲染正常。"
msgstr "Whether code blocks, internal references, and tables render correctly."

#: ../../source/contributing/translation.rst:75
#: ee5f656ff6254c57872a10bd43668f07
msgid "如果不确定某个术语怎么翻译，可以先保留 API 原名，并在 PR 中说明疑问。术语一致性比单句看起来华丽更重要。"
msgstr "If you are unsure how to translate a term, keep the API name first and explain the question in the PR. Terminology consistency matters more than making a single sentence sound polished."
